## Outputs

- `agents/{slug}/state-machine.ts` — typed state machine + exhaustive
  transition function.
- `agents/{slug}/tools.ts` — tool registry with schemas, pre/postconditions,
  error contracts.
- `agents/{slug}/prompts/{system,planning,step,reflect}.md` — versioned
  prompts.
- `agents/{slug}/EVAL.md` — pattern + tool + stopping + eval baseline.
- Paired `evals/{agent-slug}/` via `/eval-harness`.

